          "type": "body-copy",
          "settings": {
            "copy": "<p>Isopropyl Cloprostenate or \"IC\" is one of our key ingredients featured in our enhancing serums. It is a type of prostaglandin analogue that is known for hair conditioning, as defined by INCI.<br\/><br\/><strong>Did you know?<\/strong> INCI is a cosmetic ingredient dictionary & the beauty industry’s standard for recognizing and classifying cosmetic ingredients worldwide.<br\/><br\/>Why does GrandeLASH-MD utilize IC?\u2028Not all lash serums are created equally. We never settle for lackluster results & Isopropyl Cloprostenate, in conjunction with other synergistic ingredients found within our formulas, is the gold standard for the real, undeniable results you know & love.<\/p>"
          }
        }
      },
